System-to-system integration development using API, messaging and related technologies; 
Experience in full-stack web application and RESTful APIs development will be an added 
advantage; 
Experience in DevOps, Machine LearningOps will be an added advantage; 
Experience in operational support in delivering Big Data solutions will be an added advantage; 
Familiar with Linux/UNIX system administration will be an added advantage; 
Familiar with Azure Cloud or other cloud technologies will be an added advantage; 
Familiar with open-source software technologies in the Big Data solutions space will be an 
added advantage; 
Effective oral and written communication with strong analytical, problem solving, 
troubleshooting skills are essential; 
Willing to experiment the latest software tools, and integrate different software components 
